/**
 * This component will use Cloudinary to power your open graph images (and twitter). It'll automatically generate your meta tags and place them in the head of your page.
 *
 * @example
 *
 * Simple OG Image
 * ```svelte
 * <script>
 * 	import { CldOgImage } from 'svelte-cloudinary';
 * </script>
 *
 * <CldOgImage
 * 	src="images/turtle"
 * 	alt="Turtle"
 * />
 * ```
 *
 * @see
 *
 * https://svelte.cloudinary.dev/components/og-image
 */

 *

 *
 * https://svelte.cloudinary.dev/config

comment.summary: Overrides for the global Cloudinary config.

An array of tags to exclude from being created.
Currently only the `twitter:title` tag is supported.
